  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\ngenesisBuilder does some quite inefficient things:\r\n\r\n- Recompute the list of active validators for every batch of deposits: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/00a6ffab60558ecd2a84dcc976ffa0c6c0d2d16c/packages/beacon-state-transition/src/util/genesis.ts#L35\r\n- Re-hash the state every time deposits are applied https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/00a6ffab60558ecd2a84dcc976ffa0c6c0d2d16c/packages/beacon-state-transition/src/util/genesis.ts#L178\r\n- Verify deposit signatures in the multi-thread runner, to both speed it up and unfreeze the main thread\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nOptimize items listed above",
